@startuml svc-notifications--post-notifications-bulk

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #059669
    ParticipantBorderColor #374151
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
    LifeLineBorderColor #6B7280
    BoxBorderColor #94A3B8
    BoxBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
    NoteBorderColor #64748B
    NoteBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}

header [[/microservices/svc-notifications/#integration-context ⬆ svc-notifications Integration Context]]

title POST /notifications/bulk\nSend bulk notifications

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #E0F2FE
participant "svc-notifications" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-notifications/]] #F1F5F9
participant "SendGrid API" as SG [[/actors/#sendgrid-api]] #F3F4F6
participant "Twilio API" as TW [[/actors/#twilio-api]] #F3F4F6
participant "Firebase Cloud Messaging" as FCM [[/actors/#firebase-cloud-messaging]] #F3F4F6
database "PG + Valkey" as DB [[/microservices/svc-notifications/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-notifications.html#/Notifications/sendBulkNotifications View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : POST /notifications/bulk
activate GW #059669
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #059669

note right of Svc : Validate request body

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO ...
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Created row
deactivate DB

== Async Events ==

Svc ->> SG : Deliver bulk emails
Svc ->> TW : Deliver bulk SMS
Svc ->> FCM : Send bulk push notifications

Svc --> GW : 201 Created
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
deactivate GW

@enduml